text: The Dayabumi Complex is an important landmark in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia. It has many shops and offices and is one of the first skyscrapers in the city. It was officially opened on 5 May 1984, by Prime Minister Mahathir Mohamad. Category:1984 establishments in Malaysia Category:Buildings and structures in Kuala Lumpur Category:Skyscrapers in Malaysia
title: Dayabumi Complex
